episodes.title: REACTING TO MY OLD CULT VIDEO - Honor Star Crowning
episodes.description:
I’m reacting to my Honor Star Crowning ceremony video, and talking about what I did to earn this high “honor” in the Assemblies of God (AG) church. 

Subscribe for future videos about my experience in Missionettes and fundie evangelical Christianity. 

Follow me on facebook and instagram @koredevotions
